 the focused packets by atomic targets, of collision processes in\nparticle and nuclear physics, and so forth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Mar 2018 16:22:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 30 Jun 2018 16:05:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 27 Jul 2018 16:01:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-30"}
