properties\nresponsible for this result seem to be rather generic. We thus expect similar\nresults for more general, less restricted spin foam models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Mar 2018 19:49:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Apr 2018 20:09:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Sep 2018 18:11:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-20"}
