tween small and large masses. Formulating ECD\ntheory with $L_{cs}$ in NP formalism is desirable because NP formalism happens\nto be the common vocabulary for the description of low masses (Dirac theory)\nand high masses (gravity theories). A duality between Curvature and torsion has\nalso been discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Mar 2018 13:59:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Apr 2018 13:16:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-04"}
