 able to detect scientifically interpretable regions and\nconnections in the brain actively impacting the continuous response\n(creativity) in the presence of a small sample size.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Mar 2018 14:40:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-29"}
